10011.text: Happy Birthday～! I'll be hiding in the corner to make sure you have a peaceful day…

10012.text: Thank you for staying with me even though it's your birthday. I'll do my best to celebrate…!

10013.text: Birthdays are a day when even I can be the star of the show… It's a happy day when I get lots of congratulations.

10014.text: Wow, a present for me? Ugh… the fact that you remembered my birthday is already the best present ever～!

10015.text: There is a new announcement… …I often forget to look at it, so I have to check it properly…

10016.text: I received a gift! It seems no one forgot to address it like I did…!

10017.text: Congratulations on accomplishing your mission! Your trainer is amazing after all…!

10018.text: I hope I can spend the time without bothering anyone～… I hope I can spend it without bothering anyone～…

10021.text: Well… it seems that the level of the Umamusume directory has been raised.

20001.text: Ugh… just a short break… I'm an Umamusume with no physical strength… Sorry～…!

20002.text: I am different now! I was able to imitate Opera O without biting…!

20003.text: I can do anything now… Ha! I was out of line…!

20004.text: I feel like I'm doing better today… I'd like to try some things… Da, is it no good…?

20006.text: Can we move a little closer to the edge? I'm afraid to train in such a large space.

20007.text: If I start with what I can do, will I be able to grow?

20008.text: I'm so dazzled by the rest of you, more so than usual… can we really catch up…?

20009.text: Am I not pulling your leg…? I'm just causing you trouble… smh.

20010.text: I'm sorry for all my screw-ups… I'm sorry I was born…

20021.text: Huff… uh, are you going to the race? So, you are going to enter the race, right? A bad boy has to work hard…

20022.text: I'm sorry, I'm sorry…! I have to run… I have to race… but I can't move…

20024.text: Ha-ha-ha-ha!……… your spirit today is on par with that of Ms. Opera O!

20025.text: Now that I've prepared properly, I feel like I can exert more energy than usual.

20026.text: Maybe it's just my imagination, but I think I'm feeling a little better. …Just a little bit.

20028.text: At this rate… if I'm careful, it might not end badly…?

20029.text: Ha, hahi! It's a race…! I'll be careful not to fail～!

20030.text: I thought I could do my best normally. …as long as I don't get my clothes caught in the gate…

20031.text: Soooo～ hah～… Stay calm… stay calm…!

20032.text: At this rate… No, it's nothing…! I just have to do it…

20033.text: This condition… I might be a little bit worried…

20034.text: I'm sorry… I'm not feeling well～… Oh, but I'll do my best…!

20035.text: How are you doing? Perfectly fine… I'm not good at all～… But I'll try somehow…!

20036.text: I'm in a terrible state, but miracles may happen… I'll keep on running…!

20037.text: Even if you're in a slump… if you don't give up and keep running, there might be a way to save your life… right?

20050.text: I hope I didn't cause you any trouble…?

20051.text: I'll try not to drag my feet…!

90001.text: Opera O and Urara, you are always so energetic in the morning! I should learn from them too…!

90002.text: Have you eaten lunch? I… had to buy some more bread later because a bird took it away…

90003.text: I'm always sleepy after lunch… I have to make sure I don't join the next class like before…

90004.text: I feel at ease at night… I feel as if people will forgive me if I get depressed or depressed.

90005.text: Thank you for your hard work today! Tomorrow, I will do my best not to cause you any trouble…!

90007.text: I don't like summer… because it's too hot, but I like sunflowers and sparkling sunlight… I think I like those things…

90008.text: In a class assignment, we were asked, "What's your favorite autumn season?" but is there an appropriate autumn for me?

90009.text: I'm not afraid of the cold in winter. I used to live in the north when I was a child, and I have gloves and other gloves.

90010.text: Good morning! Let me show you around… Isn't today the day of the Haunted House?

90011.text: My stockings have holes…! I changed my stockings after Ms. Shakur taught me how to do it.

90012.text: Haunted houses are dark and scary… …Oh, if it was light at noon, would you be able to enjoy it even if you are scared?

90013.text: I'm sorry. The pumpkin pie I made for you all…………………………………left nothing but charcoal～～.

90014.text: It is very dark, so please be careful where you step. I fall down even if there are lights…

90015.text: Hyah! Trainer! Then the reason you ignored me when I tried to talk to you earlier… You've got the wrong person!

90016.text: The spring wind is scary, isn't it? My hat was blown off and I chased after it, only to get lost… I'm so sick of it!

90017.text: I dropped the huge pumpkin I harvested and cut it in half… I'll spend the rest of my life trying to save it～!

90018.text: What am I supposed to do as a prank…! Ugh… I'm dizzy from the pressure…!

90019.text: When I leave my hat outside on a cold day, a raccoon dog comes to hide in it. When I noticed her, she was breathing in her sleep… heh heh.

91000.text: When you are depressed, don't you feel like hiding behind something? Behind a building, behind someone…

91001.text: My parents are very kind. They said, "Dotou is a great kid"…even though that's not true at all…

91002.text: I am the King of the End of the Century! Ha-ha-ha-ha! Did I look like ………?

91003.text: I also have a relationship like that between Ms. Operao and Ms. Ayabe… No, I'm too afraid…!

91004.text: Aww… Ms. Taikishattle invited me to a party, but I think I'm out of place…?

91005.text: I don't like to wear clothes with many buttons. Because of my clumsy nature, I often misplace buttons…

91006.text: Aren't you nervous when you sing a fast-paced song? I'm afraid I'll chew…

91007.text: With this bag, I would be 100 times braver～. And strength… I hope it has that much.

91008.text: I love the bag and the ribbon on my chest, they are so cute! I feel like I will be cheered up when I wear it.

91009.text: Ugh, I thought my bag was heavy… but it wasn't my textbooks, it was my alarm clock!

91010.text: The carrot bread at the store… I'm a little curious about it, but I'm not sure I can make it if the first one to buy it wins…

91011.text: The streets at night are full of danger… I was so exhausted just going back to my dormitory…

91012.text: Cherry blossoms are dangerous… When I was walking around admiring the cherry blossoms, I hit a pillar and got a bump…

91013.text: The sea is dangerous… You may get your finger caught in a crab's mouth, or your float may be swept away……

91014.text: Yaki-imo is dangerous! If you don't let it cool down well, you'll burn your tongue like I did… hah…

91015.text: Snow is… beautiful but dangerous. I often slip and fall down hills… and become a snowman…

91016.text: I couldn't eat the candy, but I kept looking at it… and I could see my father's face in the jewelry store.

91017.text: Ms. Digital, you must be exhausted, falling down and getting up several times a day. Would it be a nuisance if I offered you something?

91018.text: Windy won't bite me. She says I'm crying too much and it's not good for me… I'm a little sad.

91019.text: Wheeeeee…! Whee～! So, is it done? Helios taught me how to do this Parisian thing…!

91021.text: My morning horoscope showed that pumpkin was my lucky item… hehehe…! Maybe something good will happen…!

91022.text: We bring snacks and sweets to the snack time with Ullala. I wonder what I should bring today…

91023.text: Recently, a cat comes to visit me at night. I wonder if they are interested in these clothes?

91024.text: Ugh… I'm a bad senior! I gently called out to a lost freshman and startled her to tears～!

91025.text: Do you have any water? I fell asleep with a pumpkin on my head and I'm sweating…!

91026.text: I… I definitely shouldn't be doing this. And yet you all look at me and say, "I'm starving…"!

91027.text: Yo, come this way if you like… The lantern is warm. How is it… is it helpful?

91028.text: When I wear a pumpkin, I feel like a different person. A little stronger, a little bigger…

91029.text: Why do crows always try to get me when I go outside? So many pumpkin crumbs!

92002.text: Sorry for the delay…! We've managed to finish preparations…!

92003.text: I'll try not to make any silly mistakes during practice, so… well, could you please guide me…?

92005.text: Even a little bit at a time… if we move forward, we can change… right?

92006.text: For the sake of my trainer who never gave up on me… I will grow even more!

92007.text: I thought I could show you a different me in training…! Maybe, just maybe… a little bit!

92011.text: But it's a training camp, and I hope you will train me hard…!

92018.text: I'm different today. My heels are comfortable to walk on, and I've only fallen once…!

92020.text: It's difficult to become the person I want to be… But I don't want to give up…!

95005.text: Oh, I don't know if I can help you…

95006.text: If I can be of any help…!

95007.text: Wow… it's like a fire was lit in my heart.

95008.text: You're guiding me all the way?

95009.text: I am the guide of souls… where am I?

95010.text: Meishoudou de suu. I believe we'll get there someday…!

110001.text: It seems like there are lots of fun stories to tell!

120000.text: It kind of… makes my heart flutter～!

400001.text: I want to bring happiness to you all in the new year…!

400004.text: What should I do? Because of my screw-up, I'm causing trouble for everyone again…

400008.text: I'm so nervous! But… I've done everything I could until today!
